Changelog
=========

The following sections provide a complete, chronologically ordered list
of all notable changes made to Pohoda-mserver-client.

When declaring a dependency on Pohoda-mserver-client, you can take
advantage of the fact that its versioning scheme dutifully follows both
the `PEP 440`_ and the `Semantic Versioning`_, version 2.0.


